      "content": "idk i feel like maybe i'm overreacting. it doesn't actually hurt, it just sounds muffled like i'm underwater in that ear. i've had stuff like this before where it just clears up after a good night of sleep. u think it's worth really going to an emergency clinic at this hour or can i just wait and see if it's fine by morning?",
